reviews.text: The restaurant with many comics pictures and very old decoration, tables and bowls are not very clean. During Saturday lunch, no need to queue. At morning, there has congee and fried noodles. No 10% surcharge. Cold drink add additional $2. Service and hygiene are better than the restaurant next to this one.

Let's see what I have eaten tonight - Steamed tofu with minced shrimp and Stir-fried vegetable-fish with Chinese black bean sauce. Yum yum yum!! I liked both of them especially the tofu! I prefer steamed food as they are healthy options... probably :P The minced shrimp balls on top of tofu were delicious because of springy texture!

The restaurant with many comics pictures and very old decoration, tables and bowls are not very clean. During Saturday lunch, no need to queue. At morning, there has congee and fried noodles. No 10% surcharge. Cold drink add additional $2. Service and hygiene are better than the restaurant next to this one.
大排檔+茶餐廳，但茶餐感覺完全被大排檔搶去

價錢和食物質素普通，可以接受。
一般港式茶餐廳，不要抱有什麼要求。
兆康苑內食肆不多，個人認為這裡是比較好的一處地方。
